programs.program:
as principal admin password "admin" do
create principal u1 "nonadmin"
create principal u2 "nonadmin"
create principal u3 "nonadmin"
set x = "x"
set delegation x admin read -> u1
set delegation x u1 read -> u2
set delegation x u2 read -> u3
set delegation x u3 read -> u1
delete delegation x admin read -> u1
return x
***

as principal u1 password "nonadmin" do
return x
***

as principal u2 password "nonadmin" do
return x
***

as principal u3 password "nonadmin" do
return x
